for what happened to the Leis.

282
00:14:51,080 --> 00:14:52,039
Xiaosu,

283
00:14:53,000 --> 00:14:54,760
if Mr. Lei didn't wake up,

284
00:14:54,880 --> 00:14:56,599
how could I explain to his son?

285
00:14:57,919 --> 00:14:59,400
We were worried that

286
00:14:59,400 --> 00:15:01,039
he could not wake up before.

287
00:15:01,200 --> 00:15:02,719
But he's awake now.

288
00:15:03,000 --> 00:15:04,960
So, we should be more confident now.

289
00:15:05,719 --> 00:15:06,799
As long as he's not well,

290
00:15:07,039 --> 00:15:08,400
