299
00:15:40,520 --> 00:15:41,400
Are you fine?

300
00:15:43,159 --> 00:15:44,119
Don't worry.

301
00:15:44,640 --> 00:15:46,000
I'm a cat

302
00:15:46,159 --> 00:15:47,280
