305
00:15:57,039 --> 00:15:58,039
On purpose?

306
00:15:58,599 --> 00:16:00,320
Are you pretending to be sick,

307
00:16:00,440 --> 00:16:01,479
as you are afraid
I'm gonna get punished?

308
00:16:03,599 --> 00:16:04,799
My heart

309
00:16:04,880 --> 00:16:05,799
