318
00:16:28,479 --> 00:16:30,679
Stanford Graduate School of Business.

319
00:16:30,760 --> 00:16:31,919
That explains.

320
00:16:31,960 --> 00:16:33,479
Your father is very far-sighted.

321
00:16:33,559 --> 00:16:34,679
