324
00:16:39,880 --> 00:16:41,080
You can't put it this way.

325
00:16:42,280 --> 00:16:44,760
You're not the only one to stumble
in the business world.

326
00:16:45,200 --> 00:16:46,159
After I

327
00:16:46,280 --> 00:16:48,280
graduated from Lancaster University
in the UK,

328
00:16:48,359 --> 00:16:49,159
I joined

329
00:16:49,239 --> 00:16:50,840
BlackRock in the UK.

330
00:16:51,119 --> 00:16:52,320
In those years,

331
00:16:52,559 --> 00:16:54,840
