332
00:16:55,799 --> 00:16:59,039
See. This is where I am.

333
00:17:00,039 --> 00:17:01,000
I haven't even asked you.

334
00:17:01,760 --> 00:17:02,880
What's the reason?

335
00:17:03,919 --> 00:17:05,799
Do you know
the Minsheng Road in Shanghai?

336
00:17:06,159 --> 00:17:07,039
I

337
00:17:07,559 --> 00:17:09,200
was the chief trader

338
00:17:09,320 --> 00:17:10,479
