339
00:17:10,559 --> 00:17:11,640
I don't need to tell you

340
00:17:12,000 --> 00:17:13,799
the rest.

341
00:17:14,719 --> 00:17:15,719
I don't get it.

342
00:17:16,719 --> 00:17:17,880
I'm just like you.

343
00:17:18,039 --> 00:17:19,440
Didn't you take all
the responsibilities on your own?

344
00:17:20,760 --> 00:17:21,280
How do you know that?

345
00:17:21,280 --> 00:17:22,840
Come out. It's time for exercise.

346
00:17:24,479 --> 00:17:26,479
We have plenty of time. Take your time.

347
00:17:53,760 --> 00:17:55,719
