from the hospital,

350
00:18:01,280 --> 00:18:02,560
we should come to see him.

351
00:18:03,400 --> 00:18:04,920
He was the president of Yutian
after all.

352
00:18:06,199 --> 00:18:07,079
Besides,

353
00:18:07,839 --> 00:18:09,239
the one I hate is Lei Yuzheng,

354
00:18:09,760 --> 00:18:10,680
not Lei Ting.

355
00:18:11,199 --> 00:18:11,760
Let's go.

356
00:18:42,800 --> 00:18:43,599
Mr. Lei.

357
00:18:44,719 --> 00:18:45,520
Mr. Lei.

358
00:18:45,640 --> 00:18:46,520
Guys.

359
00:18:48,920 --> 00:18:49,680
Hello, uncle Duan.

360
00:18:49,680 --> 00:18:50,920
