366
00:18:58,959 --> 00:18:59,920
He's awake.

367
00:19:00,520 --> 00:19:01,680
Fine. I'll leave you alone.

368
00:19:01,719 --> 00:19:03,040
I'll make you some tea.

369
00:19:03,040 --> 00:19:03,920
Go ahead.

370
00:19:06,520 --> 00:19:09,119
Mr. Lei, I'm Lin Xiangyuan.

371
00:19:09,599 --> 00:19:10,719
Do you still remember?

372
00:19:17,800 --> 00:19:18,640
Mr. Lei,

373
00:19:18,839 --> 00:19:20,520
