399
00:20:30,800 --> 00:20:31,280
Mr. Lin.

400
00:20:31,280 --> 00:20:31,760
Back off!

401
00:20:31,839 --> 00:20:32,640
Let's go.

402
00:20:32,640 --> 00:20:33,319
Back off!

403
00:20:33,760 --> 00:20:34,719
