406
00:20:39,719 --> 00:20:41,199
Back off! Or I'll shoot!

407
00:20:41,400 --> 00:20:42,119
Mr. Lei,

408
00:20:42,119 --> 00:20:43,800
you wanna hit people with the stick?

409
00:20:43,800 --> 00:20:45,160
All of you are bad guys! Bad guys!

410
00:20:45,160 --> 00:20:46,760
