411
00:20:47,560 --> 00:20:48,280
What's going on?

412
00:20:48,359 --> 00:20:49,199
Excuse me.

413
00:20:49,319 --> 00:20:51,079
Mr. Lei suffered a bad illness.

414
00:20:51,199 --> 00:20:53,400
He hasn't recovered yet.
He's still confused.

415
00:20:53,880 --> 00:20:54,880
Are you hurt?

416
00:20:54,880 --> 00:20:55,640
It's fine. It's fine.

417
00:20:55,640 --> 00:20:57,079
Yuzheng, they are all bad guys.

418
00:20:57,400 --> 00:20:58,439
They're guests.

419
00:20:58,719 --> 00:20:59,880
You're bad, too.

420
00:20:59,920 --> 00:21:01,719
Bad guy. Back off!

421
00:21:01,719 --> 00:21:02,199
Look!

422
00:21:02,199 --> 00:21:03,079
Back off! All of you!

423
00:21:03,439 --> 00:21:04,160
Good lord.

424
00:21:04,319 --> 00:21:05,839
He's yelling at everyone like this now?

425
00:21:06,479 --> 00:21:08,520
He's out of his mind sometimes.

426
00:21:08,760 --> 00:21:10,760
Let's make it another day, shall we?

427
00:21:11,359 --> 00:21:12,199
Fine.

428
00:21:12,719 --> 00:21:13,479
Ask them to leave!

429
00:21:13,920 --> 00:21:15,479
They 're gone.

430
00:21:15,640 --> 00:21:16,920
Excuse me.

431
00:21:19,520 --> 00:21:21,800
